item.title: CVE-2022-22552|2024-09-17T01:36:17.536Z -- dell -- appsync
item.description: Dell EMC AppSync versions 3.9 to 4.3 contain a clickjacking vulnerability in AppSync. A remote unauthenticated attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability to trick the victim into executing state changing operations.
